text: Ute Kumitz (born 26 February 1960) is a German rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Hanover
